I think the error is in this line of updateSnowFlakes():
```
Random random = new Random(); 
if (x + random.nextInt(3) - 1 &lt; GRID_WIDTH || x + random.nextInt(3) - 1 &gt; GRID_WIDTH) {
                        return;
