This means that the function will only ever continue if the new x = ```GRID_WIDTH```. 

To fix this, try changing it to:
```
Random random = new Random(); 
if (x + random.nextInt(3) - 1 &lt; 0 || x + random.nextInt(3) - 1 &gt; GRID_WIDTH) {
                        return;
}
```

