You can refer to a path variable (or to variables annotated with @RequestBody and @RequestHeader) in a SpEl expression using their name with a `#` sign prepended at the beginning.

    @PreAuthorize(&quot;principal.userId == #taskId&quot;)
    @GetMapping(&quot;/task/{taskId}&quot;)
